<codeline lineno="1"><highlight class="comment">/**</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="2"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@file<sp/>met.dox</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="3"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@brief<sp/>Detailed<sp/>documentation<sp/>for<sp/>the<sp/>MET<sp/>Cython<sp/>class,<sp/>a<sp/>specialized<sp/>SelectionTemplate<sp/>for<sp/>Missing<sp/>Transverse<sp/>Energy<sp/>(MET)<sp/>selections.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="4"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="5"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@page<sp/>METSelection_page<sp/>MET<sp/>Selection</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="6"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="7"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>METSelection_intro<sp/>Introduction</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="8"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`MET`<sp/>class,<sp/>implemented<sp/>in<sp/>Cython,<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>specialized<sp/>selection<sp/>template<sp/>within<sp/>the<sp/>AnalysisG<sp/>framework,<sp/>designed<sp/>for<sp/>handling<sp/>Missing<sp/>Transverse<sp/>Energy<sp/>(MET)<sp/>related<sp/>selections.<sp/>It<sp/>inherits<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>generic<sp/>`SelectionTemplate`<sp/>class,<sp/>extending<sp/>its<sp/>functionalities<sp/>to<sp/>incorporate<sp/>features<sp/>and<sp/>structures<sp/>relevant<sp/>to<sp/>MET-based<sp/>analyses.<sp/>This<sp/>class<sp/>provides<sp/>a<sp/>high-performance<sp/>interface<sp/>to<sp/>an<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>MET<sp/>object,<sp/>enabling<sp/>efficient<sp/>filtering<sp/>and<sp/>analysis<sp/>based<sp/>on<sp/>MET<sp/>properties.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="9"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="10"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>METSelection_class<sp/>The<sp/>MET<sp/>Class</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="11"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>`MET`<sp/>is<sp/>a<sp/>`cdef<sp/>class`,<sp/>indicating<sp/>its<sp/>implementation<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>Cython<sp/>extension<sp/>type.<sp/>It<sp/>inherits<sp/>from<sp/>`SelectionTemplate`,<sp/>thereby<sp/>gaining<sp/>all<sp/>the<sp/>base<sp/>functionalities<sp/>for<sp/>event<sp/>selection,<sp/>ROOT<sp/>file<sp/>interpretation,<sp/>and<sp/>weight<sp/>management.<sp/>Its<sp/>primary<sp/>role<sp/>is<sp/>to<sp/>encapsulate<sp/>a<sp/>C++<sp/>`met`<sp/>object,<sp/>which<sp/>likely<sp/>contains<sp/>the<sp/>logic<sp/>for<sp/>calculating<sp/>and<sp/>applying<sp/>selections<sp/>based<sp/>on<sp/>MET.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="12"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="13"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>METSelection_cinit_dealloc<sp/>Constructors<sp/>and<sp/>Destructors</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="14"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__cinit__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="15"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>Cython<sp/>&quot;constructor&quot;<sp/>equivalent,<sp/>called<sp/>during<sp/>object<sp/>allocation.<sp/>It<sp/>initializes<sp/>a<sp/>new<sp/>C++<sp/>`met`<sp/>object<sp/>and<sp/>assigns<sp/>its<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>`self.ptr`.<sp/>It<sp/>then<sp/>upcasts<sp/>`self.ptr`<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>`met*`<sp/>and<sp/>assigns<sp/>it<sp/>to<sp/>`self.tt`<sp/>for<sp/>specialized<sp/>access.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="16"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="17"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__init__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="18"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>(Not<sp/>explicitly<sp/>defined<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>provided<sp/>snippet)<sp/>This<sp/>would<sp/>typically<sp/>be<sp/>the<sp/>Python<sp/>initializer.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="19"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="20"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`__dealloc__(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="21"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>The<sp/>Cython<sp/>&quot;destructor&quot;<sp/>equivalent,<sp/>called<sp/>upon<sp/>object<sp/>deallocation.<sp/>It<sp/>deallocates<sp/>the<sp/>C++<sp/>`met`<sp/>object<sp/>pointed<sp/>to<sp/>by<sp/>`self.tt`,<sp/>ensuring<sp/>proper<sp/>memory<sp/>management<sp/>for<sp/>the<sp/>specialized<sp/>MET<sp/>data.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="22"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="23"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>METSelection_internal_methods<sp/>Internal<sp/>Methods</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="24"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`cdef<sp/>void<sp/>transform_dict_keys(self)`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="25"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>This<sp/>method<sp/>is<sp/>intended<sp/>to<sp/>transform<sp/>the<sp/>keys<sp/>of<sp/>internal<sp/>dictionaries.<sp/>In<sp/>this<sp/>specific<sp/>implementation,<sp/>it<sp/>converts<sp/>the<sp/>`missing_et`<sp/>member<sp/>of<sp/>the<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>`met`<sp/>object<sp/>into<sp/>a<sp/>Python<sp/>dictionary<sp/>using<sp/>`as_basic_dict`<sp/>and<sp/>assigns<sp/>it<sp/>to<sp/>`self.missing_et`.<sp/>This<sp/>is<sp/>likely<sp/>used<sp/>to<sp/>expose<sp/>MET<sp/>values<sp/>to<sp/>the<sp/>Python<sp/>layer.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="26"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="27"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@subsection<sp/>METSelection_properties<sp/>Properties</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="28"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`@property<sp/>missing_et`:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="29"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/><sp/><sp/>(Implicitly<sp/>defined<sp/>through<sp/>`transform_dict_keys`)<sp/>This<sp/>property<sp/>would<sp/>provide<sp/>access<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>dictionary<sp/>containing<sp/>MET-related<sp/>values,<sp/>converted<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>underlying<sp/>C++<sp/>`met`<sp/>object.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="30"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="31"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>@section<sp/>METSelection_cpp_interaction<sp/>C++<sp/>Interaction</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="32"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>The<sp/>`MET`<sp/>class<sp/>leverages<sp/>Cython&apos;s<sp/>capabilities<sp/>for<sp/>seamless<sp/>C++<sp/>integration:</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="33"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`cdef<sp/>class<sp/>MET`:<sp/>Declares<sp/>`MET`<sp/>as<sp/>a<sp/>Cython<sp/>extension<sp/>type.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="34"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`cdef<sp/>met<sp/>*tt`:<sp/>A<sp/>C++<sp/>pointer<sp/>to<sp/>a<sp/>`met`<sp/>object,<sp/>which<sp/>is<sp/>the<sp/>specialized<sp/>C++<sp/>implementation<sp/>for<sp/>MET<sp/>calculations<sp/>and<sp/>selections.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="35"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`self.ptr<sp/>=<sp/>new<sp/>met()`:<sp/>Initializes<sp/>the<sp/>base<sp/>`SelectionTemplate`&apos;s<sp/>C++<sp/>pointer.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="36"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`self.tt<sp/>=<sp/>&lt;met*&gt;self.ptr`:<sp/>This<sp/>line<sp/>demonstrates<sp/>C++<sp/>upcasting,<sp/>where<sp/>the<sp/>base<sp/>`SelectionTemplate`&apos;s<sp/>C++<sp/>pointer<sp/>(`self.ptr`)<sp/>is<sp/>cast<sp/>to<sp/>the<sp/>specialized<sp/>`met`<sp/>type<sp/>and<sp/>assigned<sp/>to<sp/>`self.tt`.<sp/>This<sp/>allows<sp/>`MET`<sp/>to<sp/>fulfill<sp/>the<sp/>`SelectionTemplate`<sp/>interface<sp/>while<sp/>internally<sp/>managing<sp/>its<sp/>specific<sp/>`met`<sp/>data.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="37"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`from<sp/>AnalysisG.core.selection_template<sp/>cimport<sp/>SelectionTemplate`:<sp/>Imports<sp/>the<sp/>base<sp/>`SelectionTemplate`<sp/>class,<sp/>from<sp/>which<sp/>`MET`<sp/>inherits.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="38"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*<sp/>-<sp/>`from<sp/>AnalysisG.core.tools<sp/>cimport<sp/>*`:<sp/>Imports<sp/>utility<sp/>functions<sp/>for<sp/>converting<sp/>between<sp/>C++<sp/>and<sp/>Python<sp/>data<sp/>structures,<sp/>specifically<sp/>`as_basic_dict`.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="39"><highlight class="comment"><sp/>*/</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
    </programlisting>
